snippet.title: Amber Heard in Aquaman 2 Confirms Actress and WB vs Fan to Backlash [Explained In Bangla]
snippet.description:
Amber Heard in Aquaman 2 Confirms Actress and WB vs Fan to Backlash [Explained In Bangla] 

Amber Heard confirmed return as Mera in ‘Aquaman 2

Amber Heard is embroiled in a legal battle with ex Johnny Depp who sued her for libel. The pair finalized their divorce in 2017. Depp also sued The Sun for calling him “wife beater,” following Heard’s allegations that he was abusive and violent.

Despite the legal drama between the exes, Heard will return as Mera in the next Aquaman movie.

Amber Heard filed a petition asking the judge not to give in to Johnny Depp’s request to reschedule the trial because it clashed with his upcoming film Fantastic Beasts 3. Heard pointed out that the delay of the trial would affect her because she was also set to film Aquaman 2 in February, The Sun reported.

“The papers confirm for the first time that Ms Heard is still making Aquaman 2,” The Sun noted.
#AmberHeard #Aquaman2 #DCEU
